Package com.android

Class Examples

java.lang.Object
com.android.Examples
public class Examples
extends Object
enums can't extend or be extended enums dont' allow inheritance Enums can implement an interface can't create a LOCAL enum (create an enun inside a method), you can only create an enum inside a top level class or you can create a enum inside a inner static class but not inside a normal inner class To see video tutorial for this section of code Video tutorial For all 177 videos, which cover all the topics in this course go to Complete Course Video Tutorial

    (package private) static void ex1()
    method to show basics of enums using the Season enum, also show orinal() and name() in enums
    (package private) static void ex2()
    show how a enum can override methods in both main enum body and in the enum type itself also how a enum can implement an interface
    (package private) static void ex3()
    this method shows usage of the inner enum planets that is contained with the SolarSystem class as this enum is private to the SolarSystem class it cannot be accessed outside of the class
    (package private) static void ex4()
    shows how you can use enums with switch statements, here we are using the Months enum
